Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好回击了中枢一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是场精彩的对决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薙切新总帅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓟叔叔 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在写啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写信哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在往日本寄航空信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绘里奈说想看到我的信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在没法 只好给她写很多过去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻烦人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很兴奋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 绘里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得给我写信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也没有收到绘里奈的回信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再给她写一些寄过去试试的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绘里奈真是的 明明是她自己说了想要我写信的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绘里奈多亏你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓟叔叔
